Hi Kevin,
The shop manual states after a rebuild at 1,000 miles, and every 30,000 miles 
there after.  For the latter we do it every 20,000 miles because there is no 
filter other than magnetic plugs, and several NLA as new parts in there that 
we want to last as long as posssible.
